    - rid: 1998738010735116296
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 8961519616
    m_Localized: 'Each round takes {Value} Poison damage, capped at 50. '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 1998738010735116296
  - m_Id: 821515644928
    m_Localized: Block + {Power} until your next turn.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 1998738010735116296
  - m_Id: 886208589824
    m_Localized: Each point of the applier's Speed above the bearer reduces the bearer's
      Block by {Power}.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 1998738010735116296
  - m_Id: 912007753728
    m_Localized: All the bearer's actions must target the applier. Decay with Mind.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5005393918054400
    m_Localized: Reduce {Value} Accuracy.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 1998738010735116296
  - m_Id: 5789155484389376
    m_Localized: Takes Fire damage -{Value}, Electic and Ice damage +{Value}.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 1998738010735116296
  - m_Id: 5884247608020992
    m_Localized: Evasion -{Value}, Melee action Accuracy -{Value}.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 1998738010735116296
  - m_Id: 6101176885071872
    m_Localized: 'Each round takes {Value} Fire damage, capped at 50. '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 1998738010735116296
  - m_Id: 6595601302179840
    m_Localized: Strength +{Value}, Mind -{Value}.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 1998738010735116296
  - m_Id: 10087364159340544
    m_Localized: Burning never goes below 1, and melee contact inflicts the current
      Burn stacks on the target.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 1998738010735116296
  - m_Id: 21354146466336768
    m_Localized: Chased by a lump of fire, this target get {Power} Burning each turn.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 1998738010735116296
  - m_Id: 22459278268534784
    m_Localized: Speed -{Value}.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 22592854746173440
    m_Localized: On take Fire or Ice damage, it converts to Burning or Frozen.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24211041728303104
    m_Localized: Melee and Ranged damage taken is divided by {Power}. This is twice
      effective towards Fire damage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 1998738010735116296
  - m_Id: 24212234479308800
    m_Localized: Speed -{Power}. Each turn takes {Power2} Water Internal damage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 1998738010735116296
  - m_Id: 24230684559904768
    m_Localized: Accuracy -{Value}. Your attacker -{Value} Critical Hit.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 1998738010735116296
  - m_Id: 24689865221967872
    m_Localized: Heal {Value} HP each turn.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 1998738010735116296
  - m_Id: 24944213110882304
    m_Localized: HP regeneration -{Power}, MP regeneration -{Power2}.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 1998738010735116296
  - m_Id: 31294613976133632
    m_Localized: Enemy CRT -{Value} when targeting this character.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items:
      - rid: 1998738010735116296
